description: De La Rue plc designs, manufactures, and delivers banknotes in the United Kingdom, the Middle East, Africa, Asia, the Americas, Rest of Europe, and internationally. It operates through Currency, Authentication, and Identity Solutions. The company offers printed banknotes, and polymer and security features. It also provides range of physical solutions, such as tax stamps, authentication labels, and cheques and bank cards, as well as ID security components, including polycarbonate. In addition, it offers digital solutions, such as DLR Certify, a government revenue solution; and Tracelogy for brand protection, as well as licensing platform. Further, the company provides trading and non-trading, as well as insurance services. It serves the governments, central banks, and commercial organizations. The company was founded in 1813 and is headquartered in Basingstoke, the United Kingdom.
